{
  "texts": [
    "For the Palantir pseudotime 5, we used the corresponding Python package and followed the steps outlined in its documentation.",
    "As a first step, we computed the first five diffusion components with palantir.",
    "utils.run_diffusion_maps with n_components=5.",
    "Following this, we identified the multi-scale space of the data (palantir.utils.determine_ multiscale_space) and imputed the data using MAGIC 76 (palantir.utils.",
    "run_magic_imputation)."
  ]
}